                           )].

In clinically stable adult patients with left ventricular failure or left ventricular dysfunction following myocardial infarction, valsartan tablets are indicated to reduce the risk of cardiovascular mortality                [see Clinical Studies (                  
                           Error! Hyperlink reference not valid.
                           )].

